WEBVTT

00:02:56.310 --> 00:02:58.900
Hello, gentlemen.

00:02:59.880 --> 00:03:03.010
I have come to take your lives.

00:03:04.760 --> 00:03:09.010
PIERROT LE FOU

00:04:19.160 --> 00:04:21.180
Hello, boy.

00:06:28.950 --> 00:06:32.160
Your partner sure is unlucky, Jet.

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:35.620
Well, he wasn’t all that
lucky to begin with…

00:06:35.730 --> 00:06:37.390
This case is especially bad.

00:06:37.460 --> 00:06:39.330
It would be better to not get
yourselves involved in this one.

00:06:39.400 --> 00:06:41.730
I don’t care, just answer me. Now.

00:06:42.230 --> 00:06:44.730
I’m telling you this
for your own sake, and…

00:06:44.840 --> 00:06:50.210
…if you get too involved in this,
I’m gonna get in trouble, too.

00:06:53.410 --> 00:06:54.820
You know, Bob…

00:06:55.510 --> 00:06:58.610
You’re the only person
I can rely on right now.

00:06:58.680 --> 00:07:01.350
I’ll make sure it won’t
be bad for you. So…

00:07:01.420 --> 00:07:03.550
Don’t you say that every time?

00:07:03.620 --> 00:07:08.490
Really… you always have been a guy
that likes to get into trouble…

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:11.460
All right, this is only a rumor, but…

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:15.900
Have you heard of
the name “Mad Pierrot”?

00:07:30.620 --> 00:07:33.410
There he is… the rumored mummy.

00:07:33.920 --> 00:07:37.620
So, I heard you got beaten
up by some weird guy?

00:07:38.760 --> 00:07:41.920
I recall you were sleeping
like this once before.

00:07:41.990 --> 00:07:44.790
You really haven’t shown
any improvement…

00:07:44.860 --> 00:07:46.850
Oh well, it doesn’t have
anything to do with me.

00:07:48.870 --> 00:07:52.740
Don’t you end up in situations
like that because you never behave?

00:07:53.640 --> 00:07:55.970
Well, I have nothing to do with it.

00:07:57.810 --> 00:08:01.540
So, since I have nothing to
do with it, if you’ll excuse me…

00:08:01.650 --> 00:08:02.740
Take care.

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:08.610
The victim was a high-ranking
guy from the ISSP.

00:08:08.690 --> 00:08:10.450
He was the seventh victim.

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:11.550
What did you say?

00:08:11.660 --> 00:08:15.490
Can’t blame ya. This is top-secret.

00:08:15.560 --> 00:08:20.190
Apparently those higher-ups don’t
want the world to find out about this.

00:08:20.270 --> 00:08:21.260
Why?

00:08:21.700 --> 00:08:23.400
Your partner is in deep trouble.

00:08:25.540 --> 00:08:28.270
The guy is a perfect killing machine.

00:08:28.340 --> 00:08:32.710
They say that nobody who has seen
his face has made it out alive…

00:08:33.280 --> 00:08:37.340
Even those lucky enough to escape’ll be
tracked down to the ends of the world…

00:08:37.420 --> 00:08:39.980
…and they always wind up dead.

00:08:40.390 --> 00:08:45.120
They say he appears with a smile,
and he leaves with a smile…

00:09:04.240 --> 00:09:09.740
Yeah, he is the mysterious
assassin known as Mad Pierrot…

00:09:09.820 --> 00:09:12.220
Tongpu.

00:09:55.090 --> 00:09:56.250
Faye-Faye!

00:09:56.330 --> 00:09:58.390
Puff, puff! Faye-Faye!

00:09:59.000 --> 00:10:01.560
Puff, puff! Faye-Faye…

00:10:01.630 --> 00:10:05.940
Hey you, can you stop saying
my name twice like that?

00:10:05.940 --> 00:10:08.630
Faye-Faye, a weird mail came, came.

00:10:08.710 --> 00:10:09.900
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:14.780
…and I woulda been done if
I had a little more time…

00:10:14.780 --> 00:10:15.910
I can’t read it!

00:10:17.950 --> 00:10:21.940
“Hello, boy. I’ll invite
you to a wonderful party…”

00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:24.680
Wait, this is…

00:10:24.760 --> 00:10:28.620
Listen, keep the fact that this
mail came a secret from Spike.

00:10:28.690 --> 00:10:30.030
Secret?

00:10:30.100 --> 00:10:30.960
Why?

00:10:31.030 --> 00:10:32.290
Why secret?

00:10:32.700 --> 00:10:34.190
If we don’t, that idiot…

00:10:34.270 --> 00:10:37.600
…will run out to meet him?

00:10:38.700 --> 00:10:41.970
It’s a secret, secret mail!

00:10:43.310 --> 00:10:45.280
Space Land?

00:10:45.280 --> 00:10:47.580
Pretty considerate of him
to hold the party there.

00:10:47.680 --> 00:10:49.340
You’re gonna go like that?

00:10:49.410 --> 00:10:52.210
Well, it would be perfect
if it was a masquerade.

00:10:55.020 --> 00:10:58.620
Maybe this one really
will be the end of me…

00:11:00.160 --> 00:11:02.350
Just kidding!

00:11:02.430 --> 00:11:05.090
Would you come rescue
me if I said that?

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:07.300
Idiot.

00:11:07.300 --> 00:11:10.230
Idiot, idiot, idiot!

00:11:21.450 --> 00:11:23.380
<i>Hey…</i>

00:11:23.450 --> 00:11:25.050
<i>Oh, it’s you, Ed. Where’s Spike?</i>

00:11:25.150 --> 00:11:26.620
<i>He went somewhere.</i>

00:11:26.690 --> 00:11:27.810
What?

00:11:28.350 --> 00:11:31.410
Not that this is anything new…
That idiot…

00:11:31.690 --> 00:11:33.160
Idiot, idiot?

00:11:33.230 --> 00:11:34.780
<i>Ed, I have a favor to ask.</i>

00:11:34.860 --> 00:11:36.290
What, what?

00:13:02.610 --> 00:13:03.600
Hello!

00:13:03.680 --> 00:13:04.650
Welcome!

00:13:05.320 --> 00:13:06.380
Yo…

00:13:09.190 --> 00:13:11.780
Let’s party!

00:13:39.250 --> 00:13:40.580
<i>You can’t enter here!</i>

00:13:42.120 --> 00:13:44.590
<i>It’s dangerous in here!</i>
<i>Let’s play outside!</i>

00:13:44.660 --> 00:13:46.890
<i>It’s dangerous in here!</i>
<i>Let’s play outside!</i>

00:13:46.960 --> 00:13:47.760
Shut up!

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:50.280
<i>It’s dangerous in here!</i>
<i>Let’s play outside!</i>

00:13:50.360 --> 00:13:51.620
<i>It’s dangerous in here!</i>

00:13:57.070 --> 00:13:59.200
<i>It’s dangerous in here!</i>
<i>Let’s play outside!</i>

00:14:00.870 --> 00:14:01.900
Hi!

00:14:13.520 --> 00:14:15.280
<i>All right, Ed…</i>

00:14:15.350 --> 00:14:21.350
<i>First, enter the ISSP’s main</i>
<i>computer, and look for section 13.</i>

00:14:21.460 --> 00:14:24.050
Aye, aye!

00:14:24.500 --> 00:14:28.460
That’s the section that doesn’t
exist to the general public.

00:14:28.900 --> 00:14:31.230
<i>It’s a pretty tall order…</i>
<i>Can you do it?</i>

00:14:31.300 --> 00:14:32.330
Yup!

00:15:03.400 --> 00:15:04.460
Hello!

00:15:20.390 --> 00:15:21.850
Found it!

00:15:22.750 --> 00:15:26.950
<i>After you open it, find the</i>
<i>file with the code name “Tongpu.”</i>

00:15:27.030 --> 00:15:29.190
Yup!

00:16:12.100 --> 00:16:13.140
Peek-a…

00:16:13.140 --> 00:16:15.440
…boo!

00:17:42.460 --> 00:17:46.260
<i>ISSP Assassination Ability,</i>
<i>Improvement Experiment.</i>

00:17:46.330 --> 00:17:49.390
<i>Experiment sample chart number 46.</i>

00:17:49.470 --> 00:17:51.530
<i>Code name: Tongpu.</i>

00:17:51.640 --> 00:17:54.800
<i>Confirmed a strong regression</i>
<i>of the mind during…</i>

00:17:54.870 --> 00:17:58.000
<i>…the experiment.</i>
<i>Experiment was canceled.</i>

00:17:58.080 --> 00:18:02.410
<i>Sample to be permanently kept</i>
<i>in a quarantine facility,</i>

00:18:27.270 --> 00:18:31.680
In the beginning, he escaped
from the facilities to seek revenge…

00:18:31.740 --> 00:18:35.650
…but now he seems to be enjoying
the actual act of killing.

00:18:35.710 --> 00:18:39.650
His mind must be
continuing to regress.

00:18:39.850 --> 00:18:44.380
So, he’s like a child with
superhuman fighting abilities.

00:18:44.590 --> 00:18:46.490
Really…

00:18:46.560 --> 00:18:49.620
There is nothing as pure
and cruel as children.

00:18:54.770 --> 00:18:57.460
It’s show time!

00:19:05.680 --> 00:19:06.770
That was unnecessary!

00:19:31.840 --> 00:19:34.170
<i>Hello, hello…</i>

00:19:34.510 --> 00:19:36.840
<i>Hello! Hello!</i>

00:19:36.910 --> 00:19:38.170
Hello…

00:20:56.590 --> 00:20:59.150
T-That hurts!

00:21:03.390 --> 00:21:04.920
It hurts!

00:21:06.100 --> 00:21:08.500
It hurts!!

00:21:11.570 --> 00:21:14.040
It hurts!!

00:21:14.140 --> 00:21:15.270
Hurts…

00:21:15.340 --> 00:21:20.210
Mommy, it hurts!

00:21:21.850 --> 00:21:23.970
Mommy!!

00:21:28.320 --> 00:21:32.950
It hurts… Mommy!

00:21:58.750 --> 00:22:02.190
<i>Spike! All right,</i>
<i>we figured out what he is! He’s…</i>

00:22:02.190 --> 00:22:07.020
No. I don’t need it anymore…

00:22:11.430 --> 00:22:14.920
It all ended just now…

00:22:39.870 --> 00:22:45.300
Aishiteta to nageku niwa…
Too much time has passed by…

00:22:45.340 --> 00:22:51.640
…amarinimo toki wa sugite shimatta
…to lament that we were deeply in love.

00:22:51.680 --> 00:22:57.340
Mada kokoro no hokorobi wo…
The wind keeps blowing, while my heart…

00:22:57.380 --> 00:23:04.080
…iyasenu mama kaze ga fuiteru
…cannot heal all the tears in it.

00:23:04.120 --> 00:23:13.330
Kawaita hitomi de dareka naite kure
Someone, cry for me with parched eyes.

00:23:14.930 --> 00:23:18.340
The real folk blues.

00:23:18.340 --> 00:23:26.750
Honto no kanashimi ga shiritai dake
I only want to know what true sadness is.

00:23:26.780 --> 00:23:34.380
Doro no kawa ni tsukatta…
Sitting in muddy water…

00:23:34.420 --> 00:23:38.880
…jinsei mo waruku wa nai…
…isn’t such a bad life…

00:23:38.920 --> 00:23:47.800
…ichido kiri de owaru nara…
…if it ends after the first time…

00:24:03.600 --> 00:24:04.640
COMING EPISODE

00:24:06.480 --> 00:24:09.450
I knew there was something
fishy going on lately.

00:24:09.510 --> 00:24:11.480
So, that’s what it was!

00:24:12.950 --> 00:24:14.820
What are you guys talking about?

00:24:14.890 --> 00:24:17.010
You really can’t judge
people by their looks…

00:24:17.090 --> 00:24:18.820
Honestly disgusting.

00:24:18.890 --> 00:24:21.520
Hey, hey, what are you
guys talking about?

00:24:21.590 --> 00:24:23.860
I never thought it would
be a teenage girl…

00:24:23.930 --> 00:24:25.660
It makes me despise him.

00:24:25.730 --> 00:24:27.600
Who are you talking about?

00:24:27.670 --> 00:24:29.620
Next episode: “Boogie Woogie Feng Shui”.

00:24:29.620 --> 00:24:29.630
BOOGIE WOOGIE
